channel.title: Live Tennis: ATP & WTA Queen's 2025
channel.desc: Who will add their name to the exalted list of men's winners at this celebrated grass court tennis tournament, gaining kudos and confidence ahead of Wimbledon in eight days' time? A world-class list of players entered Queen's this year, including 2023 winner and two-time defending Wimbledon champion Carlos Alcaraz and high-flying Jack Draper.
